originalText.text: DJ ShortyLove DJed my father-in-law's 65th birthday on 06/03/2023 and it was the best night ever!! Our crowd was mixed, not only in ethnic backgrounds, but also in age range and DJ ShortyLove played a great variety that catered to everyone's musical tastes. She kept people on the dance floor all night! She was very professional, courteous, and fun. I strongly recommend her for any event you may have that requires a DJ that knows her music and knows how to work a crowd. I have no upcoming events, but her vibe makes me want to plan another party just to have her DJ. Thank you for your service!!

originalText.text:
I first met DJ ShortyLove through a mutual friend in 2016. She was my DJ for my wedding. DJ Shorty Love played the best music. She caters to all ages. Everyone was on the dance floor the entire night. They loved her and raved about her for a long time.

Then in 2017, she invited me to a lounge to celebrate my birthday with her and friends as we're born the same month. My husband and I took my best friend with us. Again,  we were on the dance floor all night. DJ Shorty Love never misses a beat! She's always on point.

I would highly recommend her for any event as she is super courteous, professional and just an overall delight to be around. I've yet to see her in a bad mood. Always cheerful and friendly. She makes you feel like you've known her for years from the very 1st time meeting her. We love DJ Shorty Love, best female DJ in Harlem for sure!
